---
title: One-Pot Creamy Mushroom, Chicken & Leek Pasta with Parmesan Cheese
description: If you have your favourite pair of slippers handy, we suggest putting them on because a bowl of creamy pasta is how we’re winding down for the day. Hum in bliss when you taste the mushrooms and leek in the sauce and with only one pot it’s a dinner with no fuss and a whole lot of comfort.

*We’ve replaced the penne in this recipe with fusilli due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/666b9155f6d6f122b49fdd5e-a2480efb.jpeg
